{"tid":1593660,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政府公佈：荔枝角收押所一還押男子昨上吊自殺　今早死亡","createTime":"2019-09-25T07:21:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T08:08:32.000Z","uid":68738,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"6ae64a017877fc5bd4b5da3064aedd9d5e314a1d","tid":1593660,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T07:21:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/0_Ky6my20copy_8Chpr_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F0_Ky6my20copy_8Chpr_1200x0.png&h=d88356ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n政府公佈，荔枝角收押所一名 49 歲男性還押在囚人士昨日（ 9 月 24 日）上吊自殺，今早證實死亡。<br />\n<br />\n公佈指昨日晚上十時零四分，懲教人員發現該名在囚人士在囚室內用床單繫於囚室鐵柵上吊自殺，並立即召喚支援。支援人員到場後隨即為他進行急救及召喚救護車將他送往公立醫院搶救。他其後於今日早上十時零八分被證實死亡。<br />\n<br />\n懲教署已將事件通知警方，死因裁判法庭亦將進行死因研訊。<br />\n<br />\n公佈指死者因販運危險藥物罪而被還押。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/society/%E8%8D%94%E6%9E%9D%E8%A7%92%E6%94%B6%E6%8A%BC%E6%89%80-49-%E6%AD%B2%E9%82%84%E6%8A%BC%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E6%98%A8%E4%B8%8A%E5%90%8A%E8%87%AA%E6%AE%BA-%E4%BB%8A%E6%97%A9%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%A1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E8%258D%2594%25E6%259E%259D%25E8%25A7%2592%25E6%2594%25B6%25E6%258A%25BC%25E6%2589%2580-49-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E9%2582%2584%25E6%258A%25BC%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25AD%2590%25E6%2598%25A8%25E4%25B8%258A%25E5%2590%258A%25E8%2587%25AA%25E6%25AE%25BA-%25E4%25BB%258A%25E6%2597%25A9%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E4%25BA%25A1%2F&d=ZBayvnjX3omFcj6xyood9Mg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=a0373bde\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E8%258D%2594%25E6%259E%259D%25E8%25A7%2592%25E6%2594%25B6%25E6%258A%25BC%25E6%2589%2580-49-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E9%2582%2584%25E6%258A%25BC%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25AD%2590%25E6%2598%25A8%25E4%25B8%258A%25E5%2590%258A%25E8%2587%25AA%25E6%25AE%25BA-%25E4%25BB%258A%25E6%2597%25A9%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E4%25BA%25A1%2F&h=a83c7c